    ('25', 'Pikachu', 'Electric', NULL, '35', '55', '40', '50', '50', '90', '320', '0.4', '6.0', '112.0', 'static|lightning-rod', 'lightning-rod', 'gen-i', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'yellow', 'quadruped', 'ground|fairy', 'forest', 'medium', '190', '70', 'Mouse PokÃ©mon', '10', 'When several of these POKÃ©MON gather, their electricity could build and cause lightning storms.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/25.png'),
