    ('669', 'Flabebe', 'Fairy', NULL, '44', '38', '39', '61', '79', '42', '303', '0.1', '0.1', '61.0', 'flower-veil|symbiosis', 'symbiosis', 'gen-vi', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'white', 'arms', 'fairy', NULL, 'medium', '225', '70', 'Single Bloom PokÃ©mon', '344', 'It draws out and controls the hidden power of flowers. The flower FlabÃ©bÃ© holds is most likely part of its body.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/669.png'),
