    ('727', 'Incineroar', 'Fire', 'Dark', '95', '115', '90', '80', '90', '60', '530', '1.8', '83.0', '239.0', 'blaze|intimidate', 'intimidate', 'gen-vii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'red', 'upright', 'ground', NULL, 'medium-slow', '45', '70', 'Heel PokÃ©mon', '375', 'This PokÃ©mon has a violent, selfish disposition. If itâ€™s not in the mood to listen, it will ignore its Trainerâ€™s orders with complete nonchalance.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/727.png'),
