    ('731', 'Pikipek', 'Normal', 'Flying', '35', '75', '30', '30', '30', '65', '265', '0.3', '1.2', '53.0', 'keen-eye|skill-link|pickup', 'pickup', 'gen-vii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'black', 'wings', 'flying', NULL, 'medium', '255', '70', 'Woodpecker PokÃ©mon', '377', 'It can peck at a rate of 16 times a second to drill holes in trees. It uses the holes for food storage and for nesting.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/731.png'),
