    ('783', 'Hakamo-O', 'Dragon', 'Fighting', '55', '75', '90', '65', '70', '65', '420', '1.2', '47.0', '147.0', 'bulletproof|soundproof|overcoat', 'overcoat', 'gen-vii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'gray', 'upright', 'dragon', NULL, 'slow', '45', '70', 'Scaly PokÃ©mon', '408', 'It leaps at its prey with a courageous shout. Its scaly punches tear its opponents to shreds.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/783.png'),
    ('784', 'Kommo-O', 'Dragon', 'Fighting', '75', '110', '125', '100', '105', '85', '600', '1.6', '78.2', '270.0', 'bulletproof|soundproof|overcoat', 'overcoat', 'gen-vii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'gray', 'upright', 'dragon', NULL, 'slow', '45', '70', 'Scaly PokÃ©mon', '408', 'When it spots enemies, it threatens them by jingling the scales on its tail. Weak opponents will crack and flee in panic.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/784.png'),
    ('785', 'Tapu-Koko', 'Electric', 'Fairy', '70', '115', '85', '95', '75', '130', '570', '1.8', '20.5', '257.0', 'electric-surge|telepathy', 'telepathy', 'gen-vii', 'true', 'false', 'false', 'yellow', 'arms', 'no-eggs', NULL, 'slow', '3', '70', 'Land Spirit PokÃ©mon', '409', 'This guardian deity of Melemele is brimming with curiosity. It summons thunderclouds and stores their lightning inside its body.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/785.png'),
    ('786', 'Tapu-Lele', 'Psychic', 'Fairy', '70', '85', '75', '130', '115', '95', '570', '1.2', '18.6', '257.0', 'psychic-surge|telepathy', 'telepathy', 'gen-vii', 'true', 'false', 'false', 'pink', 'arms', 'no-eggs', NULL, 'slow', '3', '70', 'Land Spirit PokÃ©mon', '410', 'This guardian deity of Akala is guilelessly cruel. The fragrant aroma of flowers is the source of its energy.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/786.png'),
    ('787', 'Tapu-Bulu', 'Grass', 'Fairy', '70', '130', '115', '85', '95', '75', '570', '1.9', '45.5', '257.0', 'grassy-surge|telepathy', 'telepathy', 'gen-vii', 'true', 'false', 'false', 'red', 'arms', 'no-eggs', NULL, 'slow', '3', '70', 'Land Spirit PokÃ©mon', '411', 'It pulls large trees up by the roots and swings them around. It causes vegetation to grow, and then it absorbs energy from the growth.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/787.png'),
    ('788', 'Tapu-Fini', 'Water', 'Fairy', '70', '75', '115', '95', '130', '85', '570', '1.3', '21.2', '257.0', 'misty-surge|telepathy', 'telepathy', 'gen-vii', 'true', 'false', 'false', 'purple', 'arms', 'no-eggs', NULL, 'slow', '3', '70', 'Land Spirit PokÃ©mon', '412', 'The dense fog it creates brings the downfall and destruction of its confused enemies. Ocean currents are the source of its energy.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/788.png'),
    ('789', 'Cosmog', 'Psychic', NULL, '43', '29', '31', '29', '31', '37', '200', '0.2', '0.1', '40.0', 'unaware', NULL, 'gen-vii', 'true', 'false', 'false', 'blue', 'ball', 'no-eggs', NULL, 'slow', '45', '0', 'Nebula PokÃ©mon', '413', 'Its body is gaseous and frail. It slowly grows as it collects dust from the atmosphere.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/789.png'),
    ('790', 'Cosmoem', 'Psychic', NULL, '43', '29', '131', '29', '131', '37', '400', '0.1', '999.9', '140.0', 'sturdy', NULL, 'gen-vii', 'true', 'false', 'false', 'blue', 'ball', 'no-eggs', NULL, 'slow', '45', '0', 'Protostar PokÃ©mon', '413', 'Motionless as if dead, its body is faintly warm to the touch. In the distant past, it was called the cocoon of the stars.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/790.png'),
    ('791', 'Solgaleo', 'Psychic', 'Steel', '137', '137', '107', '113', '89', '97', '680', '3.4', '230.0', '306.0', 'full-metal-body', NULL, 'gen-vii', 'true', 'false', 'false', 'white', 'quadruped', 'no-eggs', NULL, 'slow', '45', '0', 'Sunne PokÃ©mon', '413', 'It is said to live in another world. The intense light it radiates from the surface of its body can make the darkest of nights light up like midday.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/791.png'),
    ('792', 'Lunala', 'Psychic', 'Ghost', '137', '113', '89', '137', '107', '97', '680', '4.0', '120.0', '306.0', 'shadow-shield', NULL, 'gen-vii', 'true', 'false', 'false', 'purple', 'wings', 'no-eggs', NULL, 'slow', '45', '0', 'Moone PokÃ©mon', '413', 'It is said to be a female evolution of Cosmog. When its third eye activates, away it flies to another world.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/792.png'),
    ('793', 'Nihilego', 'Rock', 'Poison', '109', '53', '47', '127', '131', '103', '570', '1.2', '55.5', '257.0', 'beast-boost', NULL, 'gen-vii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'white', 'tentacles', 'no-eggs', NULL, 'slow', '45', '0', 'Parasite PokÃ©mon', '414', 'One of several mysterious Ultra Beasts. People on the street report observing those infested by it suddenly becoming violent.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/793.png'),
    ('794', 'Buzzwole', 'Bug', 'Fighting', '107', '139', '139', '53', '53', '79', '570', '2.4', '333.6', '257.0', 'beast-boost', NULL, 'gen-vii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'red', 'tentacles', 'no-eggs', NULL, 'slow', '45', '0', 'Swollen PokÃ©mon', '415', 'This Ultra Beast appeared from another world. It shows off its body, but whether that display is a boast or a threat remains unclear.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/794.png'),
    ('795', 'Pheromosa', 'Bug', 'Fighting', '71', '137', '37', '137', '37', '151', '570', '1.8', '25.0', '257.0', 'beast-boost', NULL, 'gen-vii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'white', 'humanoid', 'no-eggs', NULL, 'slow', '45', '0', 'Lissome PokÃ©mon', '416', 'One of the dangerous Ultra Beasts, it has been spotted running across the land at terrific speeds.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/795.png'),
    ('796', 'Xurkitree', 'Electric', NULL, '83', '89', '71', '173', '71', '83', '570', '3.8', '100.0', '257.0', 'beast-boost', NULL, 'gen-vii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'black', 'upright', 'no-eggs', NULL, 'slow', '45', '0', 'Glowing PokÃ©mon', '417', 'One of the mysterious life-forms known as Ultra Beasts. Astonishing electric shocks emanate from its entire body, according to witnesses.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/796.png'),
    ('797', 'Celesteela', 'Steel', 'Flying', '97', '101', '103', '107', '101', '61', '570', '9.2', '999.9', '257.0', 'beast-boost', NULL, 'gen-vii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'green', 'humanoid', 'no-eggs', NULL, 'slow', '45', '0', 'Launch PokÃ©mon', '418', 'It appeared from the Ultra Wormhole. Witnesses observed it flying across the sky at high speed.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/797.png'),
    ('798', 'Kartana', 'Grass', 'Steel', '59', '181', '131', '59', '31', '109', '570', '0.3', '0.1', '257.0', 'beast-boost', NULL, 'gen-vii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'white', 'humanoid', 'no-eggs', NULL, 'slow', '45', '0', 'Drawn Sword PokÃ©mon', '419', 'This Ultra Beast came from the Ultra Wormhole. It seems not to attack enemies on its own, but its sharp body is a dangerous weapon in itself.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/798.png'),
    ('799', 'Guzzlord', 'Dark', 'Dragon', '223', '101', '53', '97', '53', '43', '570', '5.5', '888.0', '257.0', 'beast-boost', NULL, 'gen-vii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'black', 'upright', 'no-eggs', NULL, 'slow', '45', '0', 'Junkivore PokÃ©mon', '420', 'It has gobbled mountains and swallowed whole buildings, according to reports. Itâ€™s one of the Ultra Beasts.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/799.png'),
    ('800', 'Necrozma', 'Psychic', NULL, '97', '107', '101', '127', '89', '79', '600', '2.4', '230.0', '270.0', 'prism-armor', NULL, 'gen-vii', 'true', 'false', 'false', 'black', 'arms', 'no-eggs', NULL, 'slow', '255', '0', 'Prism PokÃ©mon', '421', 'Reminiscent of the Ultra Beasts, this life-form, apparently asleep underground, is thought to have come from another world in ancient times.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/800.png'),
    ('801', 'Magearna', 'Steel', 'Fairy', '80', '95', '115', '130', '115', '65', '600', '1.0', '80.5', '270.0', 'soul-heart', NULL, 'gen-vii', 'false', 'true', 'false', 'gray', 'humanoid', 'no-eggs', NULL, 'slow', '3', '0', 'Artificial PokÃ©mon', '422', 'This artificial PokÃ©mon, constructed more than 500 years ago, can understand human speech but cannot itself speak.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/801.png'),
    ('802', 'Marshadow', 'Fighting', 'Ghost', '90', '125', '80', '90', '90', '125', '600', '0.7', '22.2', '270.0', 'technician', NULL, 'gen-vii', 'false', 'true', 'false', 'gray', 'humanoid', 'no-eggs', NULL, 'slow', '3', '0', 'Gloomdweller PokÃ©mon', '423', 'Able to conceal itself in shadows, it never appears before humans, so its very existence was the stuff of myth.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/802.png'),
    ('803', 'Poipole', 'Poison', NULL, '67', '73', '67', '73', '67', '73', '420', '0.6', '1.8', '189.0', 'beast-boost', NULL, 'gen-vii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'purple', 'upright', 'no-eggs', NULL, 'slow', '45', '0', 'Poison Pin PokÃ©mon', '424', 'This Ultra Beast is well enough liked to be chosen as a first partner in its own world.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/803.png'),
