    ('813', 'Scorbunny', 'Fire', NULL, '50', '71', '40', '40', '40', '69', '310', '0.3', '4.5', '62.0', 'blaze|libero', 'libero', 'gen-viii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'white', 'upright', 'ground|humanshape', NULL, 'medium-slow', '45', '50', 'Rabbit PokÃ©mon', '431', 'A warm-up of running around gets fire energy coursing through this PokÃ©monâ€™s body. Once that happens, itâ€™s ready to fight at full power.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/813.png'),
