    ('815', 'Cinderace', 'Fire', NULL, '80', '116', '75', '65', '75', '119', '530', '1.4', '33.0', '265.0', 'blaze|libero', 'libero', 'gen-viii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'white', 'upright', 'ground|humanshape', NULL, 'medium-slow', '45', '50', 'Striker PokÃ©mon', '431', 'It juggles a pebble with its feet, turning it into a burning soccer ball. Its shots strike opponents hard and leave them scorched.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/815.png'),
    ('816', 'Sobble', 'Water', NULL, '50', '40', '40', '70', '40', '70', '310', '0.3', '4.0', '62.0', 'torrent|sniper', 'sniper', 'gen-viii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'blue', 'quadruped', 'water1|ground', NULL, 'medium-slow', '45', '50', 'Water Lizard PokÃ©mon', '432', 'When scared, this PokÃ©mon cries. Its tears pack the chemical punch of 100 onions, and attackers wonâ€™t be able to resist weeping.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/816.png'),
    ('817', 'Drizzile', 'Water', NULL, '65', '60', '55', '95', '55', '90', '420', '0.7', '11.5', '147.0', 'torrent|sniper', 'sniper', 'gen-viii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'blue', 'upright', 'water1|ground', NULL, 'medium-slow', '45', '50', 'Water Lizard PokÃ©mon', '432', 'A clever combatant, this PokÃ©mon battles using water balloons created with moisture secreted from its palms.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/817.png'),
    ('818', 'Inteleon', 'Water', NULL, '70', '85', '65', '125', '65', '120', '530', '1.9', '45.2', '265.0', 'torrent|sniper', 'sniper', 'gen-viii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'blue', 'upright', 'water1|ground', NULL, 'medium-slow', '45', '50', 'Secret Agent PokÃ©mon', '432', 'It has many hidden capabilities, such as fingertips that can shoot water and a membrane on its back that it can use to glide through the air.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/818.png'),
    ('819', 'Skwovet', 'Normal', NULL, '70', '55', '55', '35', '35', '25', '275', '0.3', '2.5', '55.0', 'cheek-pouch|gluttony', 'gluttony', 'gen-viii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'brown', 'upright', 'ground', NULL, 'medium', '255', '50', 'Cheeky PokÃ©mon', '433', 'Found throughout the Galar region, this PokÃ©mon becomes uneasy if its cheeks are ever completely empty of berries.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/819.png'),
    ('820', 'Greedent', 'Normal', NULL, '120', '95', '95', '55', '75', '20', '460', '0.6', '6.0', '161.0', 'cheek-pouch|gluttony', 'gluttony', 'gen-viii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'brown', 'upright', 'ground', NULL, 'medium', '90', '50', 'Greedy PokÃ©mon', '433', 'It stashes berries in its tailâ€”so many berries that they fall out constantly. But this PokÃ©mon is a bit slow-witted, so it doesnâ€™t notice the loss.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/820.png'),
    ('821', 'Rookidee', 'Flying', NULL, '38', '47', '35', '33', '35', '57', '245', '0.2', '1.8', '49.0', 'keen-eye|unnerve|big-pecks', 'big-pecks', 'gen-viii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'blue', 'wings', 'flying', NULL, 'medium-slow', '255', '50', 'Tiny Bird PokÃ©mon', '434', 'It will bravely challenge any opponent, no matter how powerful. This PokÃ©mon benefits from every battleâ€”even a defeat increases its strength a bit.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/821.png'),
    ('822', 'Corvisquire', 'Flying', NULL, '68', '67', '55', '43', '55', '77', '365', '0.8', '16.0', '128.0', 'keen-eye|unnerve|big-pecks', 'big-pecks', 'gen-viii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'blue', 'wings', 'flying', NULL, 'medium-slow', '120', '50', 'Raven PokÃ©mon', '434', 'Smart enough to use tools in battle, these PokÃ©mon have been seen picking up rocks and flinging them or using ropes to wrap up enemies.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/822.png'),
    ('823', 'Corviknight', 'Flying', 'Steel', '98', '87', '105', '53', '85', '67', '495', '2.2', '75.0', '248.0', 'pressure|unnerve|mirror-armor', 'mirror-armor', 'gen-viii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'purple', 'wings', 'flying', NULL, 'medium-slow', '45', '50', 'Raven PokÃ©mon', '434', 'This PokÃ©mon reigns supreme in the skies of the Galar region. The black luster of its steel body could drive terror into the heart of any foe.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/823.png'),
    ('824', 'Blipbug', 'Bug', NULL, '25', '20', '20', '25', '45', '45', '180', '0.4', '8.0', '36.0', 'swarm|compound-eyes|telepathy', 'telepathy', 'gen-viii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'blue', 'armor', 'bug', NULL, 'medium', '255', '50', 'Larva PokÃ©mon', '435', 'A constant collector of information, this PokÃ©mon is very smart. Very strong is what it isnâ€™t.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/824.png'),
    ('825', 'Dottler', 'Bug', 'Psychic', '50', '35', '80', '50', '90', '30', '335', '0.4', '19.5', '117.0', 'swarm|compound-eyes|telepathy', 'telepathy', 'gen-viii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'yellow', 'armor', 'bug', NULL, 'medium', '120', '50', 'Radome PokÃ©mon', '435', 'It barely moves, but itâ€™s still alive. Hiding in its shell without food or water seems to have awakened its psychic powers.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/825.png'),
    ('826', 'Orbeetle', 'Bug', 'Psychic', '60', '45', '110', '80', '120', '90', '505', '0.4', '40.8', '253.0', 'swarm|frisk|telepathy', 'telepathy', 'gen-viii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'red', 'wings', 'bug', NULL, 'medium', '45', '50', 'Seven Spot PokÃ©mon', '435', 'Itâ€™s famous for its high level of intelligence, and the large size of its brain is proof that it also possesses immense psychic power.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/826.png'),
    ('827', 'Nickit', 'Dark', NULL, '40', '28', '28', '47', '52', '50', '245', '0.6', '8.9', '49.0', 'run-away|unburden|stakeout', 'stakeout', 'gen-viii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'brown', 'quadruped', 'ground', NULL, 'fast', '255', '50', 'Fox PokÃ©mon', '436', 'Aided by the soft pads on its feet, it silently raids the food stores of other PokÃ©mon. It survives off its ill-gotten gains.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/827.png'),
    ('828', 'Thievul', 'Dark', NULL, '70', '58', '58', '87', '92', '90', '455', '1.2', '19.9', '159.0', 'run-away|unburden|stakeout', 'stakeout', 'gen-viii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'brown', 'quadruped', 'ground', NULL, 'fast', '127', '50', 'Fox PokÃ©mon', '436', 'It secretly marks potential targets with a scent. By following the scent, it stalks its targets and steals from them when they least expect it.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/828.png'),
    ('829', 'Gossifleur', 'Grass', NULL, '40', '40', '60', '40', '60', '10', '250', '0.4', '2.2', '50.0', 'cotton-down|regenerator|effect-spore', 'effect-spore', 'gen-viii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'green', 'blob', 'plant', NULL, 'medium', '190', '50', 'Flowering PokÃ©mon', '437', 'It anchors itself in the ground with its single leg, then basks in the sun. After absorbing enough sunlight, its petals spread as it blooms brilliantly.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/829.png'),
    ('830', 'Eldegoss', 'Grass', NULL, '60', '50', '90', '80', '120', '60', '460', '0.5', '2.5', '161.0', 'cotton-down|regenerator|effect-spore', 'effect-spore', 'gen-viii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'green', 'blob', 'plant', NULL, 'medium', '75', '50', 'Cotton Bloom PokÃ©mon', '437', 'The seeds attached to its cotton fluff are full of nutrients. It spreads them on the wind so that plants and other PokÃ©mon can benefit from them.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/830.png'),
    ('831', 'Wooloo', 'Normal', NULL, '42', '40', '55', '40', '45', '48', '270', '0.6', '6.0', '122.0', 'fluffy|run-away|bulletproof', 'bulletproof', 'gen-viii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'white', 'quadruped', 'ground', NULL, 'medium', '255', '50', 'Sheep PokÃ©mon', '438', 'Its curly fleece is such an effective cushion that this PokÃ©mon could fall off a cliff and stand right back up at the bottom, unharmed.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/831.png'),
    ('832', 'Dubwool', 'Normal', NULL, '72', '80', '100', '60', '90', '88', '490', '1.3', '43.0', '172.0', 'fluffy|steadfast|bulletproof', 'bulletproof', 'gen-viii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'white', 'quadruped', 'ground', NULL, 'medium', '127', '50', 'Sheep PokÃ©mon', '438', 'Weave a carpet from its springy wool, and you end up with something closer to a trampoline. Youâ€™ll start to bounce the moment you set foot on it.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/832.png'),
    ('833', 'Chewtle', 'Water', NULL, '50', '64', '50', '38', '38', '44', '284', '0.3', '8.5', '57.0', 'strong-jaw|shell-armor|swift-swim', 'swift-swim', 'gen-viii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'green', 'quadruped', 'monster|water1', NULL, 'medium', '255', '50', 'Snapping PokÃ©mon', '439', 'Apparently the itch of its teething impels it to snap its jaws at anything in front of it.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/833.png'),
    ('834', 'Drednaw', 'Water', 'Rock', '90', '115', '90', '48', '68', '74', '485', '1.0', '115.5', '170.0', 'strong-jaw|shell-armor|swift-swim', 'swift-swim', 'gen-viii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'green', 'quadruped', 'monster|water1', NULL, 'medium', '75', '50', 'Bite PokÃ©mon', '439', 'With jaws that can shear through steel rods, this highly aggressive PokÃ©mon chomps down on its unfortunate prey.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/834.png'),
    ('835', 'Yamper', 'Electric', NULL, '59', '45', '50', '40', '50', '26', '270', '0.3', '13.5', '54.0', 'ball-fetch|rattled', 'rattled', 'gen-viii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'yellow', 'quadruped', 'ground', NULL, 'fast', '255', '50', 'Puppy PokÃ©mon', '440', 'This PokÃ©mon is very popular as a herding dog in the Galar region. As it runs, it generates electricity from the base of its tail.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/835.png'),
    ('836', 'Boltund', 'Electric', NULL, '69', '90', '60', '90', '60', '121', '490', '1.0', '34.0', '172.0', 'strong-jaw|competitive', 'competitive', 'gen-viii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'yellow', 'quadruped', 'ground', NULL, 'fast', '45', '50', 'Dog PokÃ©mon', '440', 'This PokÃ©mon generates electricity and channels it into its legs to keep them going strong. Boltund can run nonstop for three full days.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/836.png'),
    ('837', 'Rolycoly', 'Rock', NULL, '30', '40', '50', '40', '50', '30', '240', '0.3', '12.0', '48.0', 'steam-engine|heatproof|flash-fire', 'flash-fire', 'gen-viii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'black', 'ball', 'mineral', NULL, 'medium-slow', '255', '50', 'Coal PokÃ©mon', '441', 'Most of its body has the same composition as coal. Fittingly, this PokÃ©mon was first discovered in coal mines about 400 years ago.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/837.png'),
    ('838', 'Carkol', 'Rock', 'Fire', '80', '60', '90', '60', '70', '50', '410', '1.1', '78.0', '144.0', 'steam-engine|flame-body|flash-fire', 'flash-fire', 'gen-viii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'black', 'legs', 'mineral', NULL, 'medium-slow', '120', '50', 'Coal PokÃ©mon', '441', 'It forms coal inside its body. Coal dropped by this PokÃ©mon once helped fuel the lives of people in the Galar region.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/838.png'),
    ('839', 'Coalossal', 'Rock', 'Fire', '110', '80', '120', '80', '90', '30', '510', '2.8', '310.5', '255.0', 'steam-engine|flame-body|flash-fire', 'flash-fire', 'gen-viii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'black', 'humanoid', 'mineral', NULL, 'medium-slow', '45', '50', 'Coal PokÃ©mon', '441', 'Itâ€™s usually peaceful, but the vandalism of mines enrages it. Offenders will be incinerated with flames that reach 2,700 degrees Fahrenheit.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/839.png'),
    ('840', 'Applin', 'Grass', 'Dragon', '40', '40', '80', '40', '40', '20', '260', '0.2', '0.5', '52.0', 'ripen|gluttony|bulletproof', 'bulletproof', 'gen-viii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'green', 'squiggle', 'plant|dragon', NULL, 'slow-then-very-fast', '255', '50', 'Apple Core PokÃ©mon', '442', 'It spends its entire life inside an apple. It hides from its natural enemies, bird PokÃ©mon, by pretending itâ€™s just an apple and nothing more.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/840.png'),
    ('841', 'Flapple', 'Grass', 'Dragon', '70', '110', '80', '95', '60', '70', '485', '0.3', '1.0', '170.0', 'ripen|gluttony|hustle', 'hustle', 'gen-viii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'green', 'wings', 'plant|dragon', NULL, 'slow-then-very-fast', '45', '50', 'Apple Wing PokÃ©mon', '442', 'It ate a sour apple, and that induced its evolution. In its cheeks, it stores an acid capable of causing chemical burns.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/841.png'),
    ('842', 'Appletun', 'Grass', 'Dragon', '110', '85', '80', '100', '80', '30', '485', '0.4', '13.0', '170.0', 'ripen|gluttony|thick-fat', 'thick-fat', 'gen-viii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'green', 'quadruped', 'plant|dragon', NULL, 'slow-then-very-fast', '45', '50', 'Apple Nectar PokÃ©mon', '442', 'Eating a sweet apple caused its evolution. A nectarous scent wafts from its body, luring in the bug PokÃ©mon it preys on.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/842.png'),
    ('843', 'Silicobra', 'Ground', NULL, '52', '57', '75', '35', '50', '46', '315', '2.2', '7.6', '63.0', 'sand-spit|shed-skin|sand-veil', 'sand-veil', 'gen-viii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'green', 'squiggle', 'ground|dragon', NULL, 'medium', '255', '50', 'Sand Snake PokÃ©mon', '443', 'As it digs, it swallows sand and stores it in its neck pouch. The pouch can hold more than 17 pounds of sand.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/843.png'),
    ('844', 'Sandaconda', 'Ground', NULL, '72', '107', '125', '65', '70', '71', '510', '3.8', '65.5', '179.0', 'sand-spit|shed-skin|sand-veil', 'sand-veil', 'gen-viii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'green', 'squiggle', 'ground|dragon', NULL, 'medium', '120', '50', 'Sand Snake PokÃ©mon', '443', 'When it contracts its body, over 220 pounds of sand sprays from its nose. If it ever runs out of sand, it becomes disheartened.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/844.png'),
    ('845', 'Cramorant', 'Flying', 'Water', '70', '85', '55', '85', '95', '85', '475', '0.8', '18.0', '166.0', 'gulp-missile', NULL, 'gen-viii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'blue', 'wings', 'water1|flying', NULL, 'medium', '45', '50', 'Gulp PokÃ©mon', '444', 'Itâ€™s so strong that it can knock out some opponents in a single hit, but it also may forget what itâ€™s battling midfight.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/845.png'),
    ('846', 'Arrokuda', 'Water', NULL, '41', '63', '40', '40', '30', '66', '280', '0.5', '1.0', '56.0', 'swift-swim|propeller-tail', 'propeller-tail', 'gen-viii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'brown', 'fish', 'water2', NULL, 'slow', '255', '50', 'Rush PokÃ©mon', '445', 'If it sees any movement around it, this PokÃ©mon charges for it straightaway, leading with its sharply pointed jaw. Itâ€™s very proud of that jaw.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/846.png'),
    ('847', 'Barraskewda', 'Water', NULL, '61', '123', '60', '60', '50', '136', '490', '1.3', '30.0', '172.0', 'swift-swim|propeller-tail', 'propeller-tail', 'gen-viii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'brown', 'fish', 'water2', NULL, 'slow', '60', '50', 'Skewer PokÃ©mon', '445', 'This PokÃ©mon has a jaw thatâ€™s as sharp as a spear and as strong as steel. Apparently Barraskewdaâ€™s flesh is surprisingly tasty, too.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/847.png'),
    ('848', 'Toxel', 'Electric', 'Poison', '40', '38', '35', '54', '35', '40', '242', '0.4', '11.0', '48.0', 'rattled|static|klutz', 'klutz', 'gen-viii', 'false', 'false', 'true', 'purple', 'upright', 'no-eggs', NULL, 'medium-slow', '75', '50', 'Baby PokÃ©mon', '446', 'It stores poison in an internal poison sac and secretes that poison through its skin. If you touch this PokÃ©mon, a tingling sensation follows.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/848.png'),
    ('849', 'Toxtricity-Amped', 'Electric', 'Poison', '75', '98', '70', '114', '70', '75', '502', '1.6', '40.0', '176.0', 'punk-rock|plus|technician', 'technician', 'gen-viii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'purple', 'upright', 'humanshape', NULL, 'medium-slow', '45', '50', 'Punk PokÃ©mon', '446', 'When this PokÃ©mon sounds as if itâ€™s strumming a guitar, itâ€™s actually clawing at the protrusions on its chest to generate electricity.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/849.png'),
    ('850', 'Sizzlipede', 'Fire', 'Bug', '50', '65', '45', '50', '50', '45', '305', '0.7', '1.0', '61.0', 'flash-fire|white-smoke|flame-body', 'flame-body', 'gen-viii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'red', 'tentacles', 'bug', NULL, 'medium', '190', '50', 'Radiator PokÃ©mon', '447', 'It stores flammable gas in its body and uses it to generate heat. The yellow sections on its belly get particularly hot.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/850.png'),
    ('851', 'Centiskorch', 'Fire', 'Bug', '100', '115', '65', '90', '90', '65', '525', '3.0', '120.0', '184.0', 'flash-fire|white-smoke|flame-body', 'flame-body', 'gen-viii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'red', 'tentacles', 'bug', NULL, 'medium', '75', '50', 'Radiator PokÃ©mon', '447', 'When it heats up, its body temperature reaches about 1,500 degrees Fahrenheit. It lashes its body like a whip and launches itself at enemies.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/851.png'),
    ('852', 'Clobbopus', 'Fighting', NULL, '50', '68', '60', '50', '50', '32', '310', '0.6', '4.0', '62.0', 'limber|technician', 'technician', 'gen-viii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'brown', 'tentacles', 'water1|humanshape', NULL, 'medium-slow', '180', '50', 'Tantrum PokÃ©mon', '448', 'Itâ€™s very curious, but its means of investigating things is to try to punch them with its tentacles. The search for food is what brings it onto land.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/852.png'),
    ('853', 'Grapploct', 'Fighting', NULL, '80', '118', '90', '70', '80', '42', '480', '1.6', '39.0', '168.0', 'limber|technician', 'technician', 'gen-viii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'blue', 'tentacles', 'water1|humanshape', NULL, 'medium-slow', '45', '50', 'Jujitsu PokÃ©mon', '448', 'A body made up of nothing but muscle makes the grappling moves this PokÃ©mon performs with its tentacles tremendously powerful.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/853.png'),
    ('854', 'Sinistea', 'Ghost', NULL, '40', '45', '45', '74', '54', '50', '308', '0.1', '0.2', '62.0', 'weak-armor|cursed-body', 'cursed-body', 'gen-viii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'purple', 'ball', 'mineral|indeterminate', NULL, 'medium', '120', '50', 'Black Tea PokÃ©mon', '449', 'This PokÃ©mon is said to have been born when a lonely spirit possessed a cold, leftover cup of tea.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/854.png'),
    ('855', 'Polteageist', 'Ghost', NULL, '60', '65', '65', '134', '114', '70', '508', '0.2', '0.4', '178.0', 'weak-armor|cursed-body', 'cursed-body', 'gen-viii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'purple', 'ball', 'mineral|indeterminate', NULL, 'medium', '60', '50', 'Black Tea PokÃ©mon', '449', 'This species lives in antique teapots. Most pots are forgeries, but on rare occasions, an authentic work is found.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/855.png'),
    ('856', 'Hatenna', 'Psychic', NULL, '42', '30', '45', '56', '53', '39', '265', '0.4', '3.4', '53.0', 'healer|anticipation|magic-bounce', 'magic-bounce', 'gen-viii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'pink', 'legs', 'fairy', NULL, 'slow', '235', '50', 'Calm PokÃ©mon', '450', 'Via the protrusion on its head, it senses other creaturesâ€™ emotions. If you donâ€™t have a calm disposition, it will never warm up to you.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/856.png'),
