    ('858', 'Hatterene', 'Psychic', 'Fairy', '57', '90', '95', '136', '103', '29', '510', '2.1', '5.1', '255.0', 'healer|anticipation|magic-bounce', 'magic-bounce', 'gen-viii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'pink', 'blob', 'fairy', NULL, 'slow', '45', '50', 'Silent PokÃ©mon', '450', 'It emits psychic power strong enough to cause headaches as a deterrent to the approach of others.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/858.png'),
    ('859', 'Impidimp', 'Dark', 'Fairy', '45', '45', '30', '55', '40', '50', '265', '0.4', '5.5', '53.0', 'prankster|frisk|pickpocket', 'pickpocket', 'gen-viii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'pink', 'humanoid', 'fairy|humanshape', NULL, 'medium', '255', '50', 'Wily PokÃ©mon', '451', 'Through its nose, it sucks in the emanations produced by people and PokÃ©mon when they feel annoyed. It thrives off this negative energy.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/859.png'),
    ('860', 'Morgrem', 'Dark', 'Fairy', '65', '60', '45', '75', '55', '70', '370', '0.8', '12.5', '130.0', 'prankster|frisk|pickpocket', 'pickpocket', 'gen-viii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'pink', 'humanoid', 'fairy|humanshape', NULL, 'medium', '120', '50', 'Devious PokÃ©mon', '451', 'When it gets down on all fours as if to beg for forgiveness, itâ€™s trying to lure opponents in so that it can stab them with its spear-like hair.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/860.png'),
    ('861', 'Grimmsnarl', 'Dark', 'Fairy', '95', '120', '65', '95', '75', '60', '510', '1.5', '61.0', '255.0', 'prankster|frisk|pickpocket', 'pickpocket', 'gen-viii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'purple', 'humanoid', 'fairy|humanshape', NULL, 'medium', '45', '50', 'Bulk Up PokÃ©mon', '451', 'With the hair wrapped around its body helping to enhance its muscles, this PokÃ©mon can overwhelm even Machamp.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/861.png'),
    ('862', 'Obstagoon', 'Dark', 'Normal', '93', '90', '101', '60', '81', '95', '520', '1.6', '46.0', '260.0', 'reckless|guts|defiant', 'defiant', 'gen-viii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'gray', 'upright', 'ground', NULL, 'medium', '45', '50', 'Blocking PokÃ©mon', '134', 'Its voice is staggering in volume. Obstagoon has a tendency to take on a threatening posture and shoutâ€”this move is known as Obstruct.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/862.png'),
    ('863', 'Perrserker', 'Steel', NULL, '70', '110', '100', '50', '60', '50', '440', '0.8', '28.0', '154.0', 'battle-armor|tough-claws|steely-spirit', 'steely-spirit', 'gen-viii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'brown', 'upright', 'ground', NULL, 'medium', '90', '50', 'Viking PokÃ©mon', '22', 'What appears to be an iron helmet is actually hardened hair. This PokÃ©mon lives for the thrill of battle.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/863.png'),
    ('864', 'Cursola', 'Ghost', NULL, '60', '95', '50', '145', '130', '30', '510', '1.0', '0.4', '179.0', 'weak-armor|perish-body', 'perish-body', 'gen-viii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'white', 'arms', 'water1|water3', NULL, 'fast', '30', '50', 'Coral PokÃ©mon', '113', 'Its shell is overflowing with its heightened otherworldly energy. The ectoplasm serves as protection for this PokÃ©monâ€™s core spirit.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/864.png'),
