    ('876', 'Indeedee-Male', 'Psychic', 'Normal', '60', '65', '55', '105', '95', '95', '475', '0.9', '28.0', '166.0', 'inner-focus|synchronize|psychic-surge', 'psychic-surge', 'gen-viii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'purple', 'upright', 'fairy', NULL, 'fast', '30', '140', 'Emotion PokÃ©mon', '458', 'It uses the horns on its head to sense the emotions of others. Males will act as valets for those they serve, looking after their every need.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/876.png'),
    ('877', 'Morpeko-Full-Belly', 'Electric', 'Dark', '58', '95', '58', '70', '58', '97', '436', '0.3', '3.0', '153.0', 'hunger-switch', NULL, 'gen-viii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'yellow', 'humanoid', 'ground|fairy', NULL, 'medium', '180', '50', 'Two-Sided PokÃ©mon', '459', 'As it eats the seeds stored up in its pocket-like pouches, this PokÃ©mon is not just satisfying its constant hunger. Itâ€™s also generating electricity.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/877.png'),
    ('878', 'Cufant', 'Steel', NULL, '72', '80', '49', '40', '49', '40', '330', '1.2', '100.0', '66.0', 'sheer-force|heavy-metal', 'heavy-metal', 'gen-viii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'yellow', 'quadruped', 'ground|mineral', NULL, 'medium', '190', '50', 'Copperderm PokÃ©mon', '460', 'It digs up the ground with its trunk. Itâ€™s also very strong, being able to carry loads of over five tons without any problem at all.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/878.png'),
    ('879', 'Copperajah', 'Steel', NULL, '122', '130', '69', '80', '69', '30', '500', '3.0', '650.0', '175.0', 'sheer-force|heavy-metal', 'heavy-metal', 'gen-viii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'green', 'quadruped', 'ground|mineral', NULL, 'medium', '90', '50', 'Copperderm PokÃ©mon', '460', 'They came over from another region long ago and worked together with humans. Their green skin is resistant to water.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/879.png'),
    ('880', 'Dracozolt', 'Electric', 'Dragon', '90', '100', '90', '80', '70', '75', '505', '1.8', '190.0', '177.0', 'volt-absorb|hustle|sand-rush', 'sand-rush', 'gen-viii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'green', 'upright', 'no-eggs', NULL, 'slow', '45', '50', 'Fossil PokÃ©mon', '461', 'In ancient times, it was unbeatable thanks to its powerful lower body, but it went extinct anyway after it depleted all its plant-based food sources.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/880.png'),
    ('881', 'Arctozolt', 'Electric', 'Ice', '90', '100', '90', '90', '80', '55', '505', '2.3', '150.0', '177.0', 'volt-absorb|static|slush-rush', 'slush-rush', 'gen-viii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'blue', 'upright', 'no-eggs', NULL, 'slow', '45', '50', 'Fossil PokÃ©mon', '462', 'The shaking of its freezing upper half is what generates its electricity. It has a hard time walking around.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/881.png'),
    ('882', 'Dracovish', 'Water', 'Dragon', '90', '90', '100', '70', '80', '75', '505', '2.3', '215.0', '177.0', 'water-absorb|strong-jaw|sand-rush', 'sand-rush', 'gen-viii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'green', 'legs', 'no-eggs', NULL, 'slow', '45', '50', 'Fossil PokÃ©mon', '463', 'Powerful legs and jaws made it the apex predator of its time. Its own overhunting of its prey was what drove it to extinction.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/882.png'),
    ('883', 'Arctovish', 'Water', 'Ice', '90', '90', '100', '80', '90', '55', '505', '2.0', '175.0', '177.0', 'water-absorb|ice-body|slush-rush', 'slush-rush', 'gen-viii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'blue', 'fish', 'no-eggs', NULL, 'slow', '45', '50', 'Fossil PokÃ©mon', '464', 'Though itâ€™s able to capture prey by freezing its surroundings, it has trouble eating the prey afterward because its mouth is on top of its head.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/883.png'),
    ('884', 'Duraludon', 'Steel', 'Dragon', '70', '95', '115', '120', '50', '85', '535', '1.8', '40.0', '187.0', 'light-metal|heavy-metal|stalwart', 'stalwart', 'gen-viii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'white', 'upright', 'mineral|dragon', NULL, 'medium', '45', '50', 'Alloy PokÃ©mon', '465', 'Its body resembles polished metal, and itâ€™s both lightweight and strong. The only drawback is that it rusts easily.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/884.png'),
    ('885', 'Dreepy', 'Dragon', 'Ghost', '28', '60', '30', '40', '30', '82', '270', '0.5', '2.0', '54.0', 'clear-body|infiltrator|cursed-body', 'cursed-body', 'gen-viii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'green', 'squiggle', 'indeterminate|dragon', NULL, 'slow', '45', '50', 'Lingering PokÃ©mon', '466', 'After being reborn as a ghost PokÃ©mon, Dreepy wanders the areas it used to inhabit back when it was alive in prehistoric seas.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/885.png'),
    ('886', 'Drakloak', 'Dragon', 'Ghost', '68', '80', '50', '60', '50', '102', '410', '1.4', '11.0', '144.0', 'clear-body|infiltrator|cursed-body', 'cursed-body', 'gen-viii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'green', 'arms', 'indeterminate|dragon', NULL, 'slow', '45', '50', 'Caretaker PokÃ©mon', '466', 'Itâ€™s capable of flying faster than 120 mph. It battles alongside Dreepy and dotes on them until they successfully evolve.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/886.png'),
    ('887', 'Dragapult', 'Dragon', 'Ghost', '88', '120', '75', '100', '75', '142', '600', '3.0', '50.0', '300.0', 'clear-body|infiltrator|cursed-body', 'cursed-body', 'gen-viii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'green', 'upright', 'indeterminate|dragon', NULL, 'slow', '45', '50', 'Stealth PokÃ©mon', '466', 'When it isnâ€™t battling, it keeps Dreepy in the holes on its horns. Once a fight starts, it launches the Dreepy like supersonic missiles.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/887.png'),
    ('888', 'Zacian', 'Fairy', NULL, '92', '120', '115', '80', '115', '138', '660', '2.8', '110.0', '335.0', 'intrepid-sword', NULL, 'gen-viii', 'true', 'false', 'false', 'blue', 'quadruped', 'no-eggs', NULL, 'slow', '10', '0', 'Warrior PokÃ©mon', '467', 'Known as a legendary hero, this PokÃ©mon absorbs metal particles, transforming them into a weapon it uses to battle.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/888.png'),
    ('889', 'Zamazenta', 'Fighting', NULL, '92', '120', '115', '80', '115', '138', '660', '2.9', '210.0', '335.0', 'dauntless-shield', NULL, 'gen-viii', 'true', 'false', 'false', 'red', 'quadruped', 'no-eggs', NULL, 'slow', '10', '0', 'Warrior PokÃ©mon', '468', 'In times past, it worked together with a king of the people to save the Galar region. It absorbs metal that it then uses in battle.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/889.png'),
