    ('891', 'Kubfu', 'Fighting', NULL, '60', '90', '60', '53', '50', '72', '385', '0.6', '12.0', '77.0', 'inner-focus', NULL, 'gen-viii', 'true', 'false', 'false', 'gray', 'upright', 'no-eggs', NULL, 'slow', '3', '50', 'Wushu PokÃ©mon', '470', 'Kubfu trains hard to perfect its moves. The moves it masters will determine which form it takes when it evolves.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/891.png'),
    ('892', 'Urshifu-Single-Strike', 'Fighting', 'Dark', '100', '130', '100', '63', '60', '97', '550', '1.9', '105.0', '275.0', 'unseen-fist', NULL, 'gen-viii', 'true', 'false', 'false', 'gray', 'humanoid', 'no-eggs', NULL, 'slow', '3', '50', 'Wushu PokÃ©mon', '470', 'This form of Urshifu is a strong believer in the one-hit KO. Its strategy is to leap in close to foes and land a devastating blow with a hardened fist.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/892.png'),
    ('893', 'Zarude', 'Dark', 'Grass', '105', '120', '105', '70', '95', '105', '600', '1.8', '70.0', '300.0', 'leaf-guard', NULL, 'gen-viii', 'false', 'true', 'false', 'green', 'upright', 'no-eggs', NULL, 'slow', '3', '0', 'Rogue Monkey PokÃ©mon', '471', 'Within dense forests, this PokÃ©mon lives in a pack with others of its kind. Itâ€™s incredibly aggressive, and the other PokÃ©mon of the forest fear it.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/893.png'),
    ('894', 'Regieleki', 'Electric', NULL, '80', '100', '50', '100', '50', '200', '580', '1.2', '145.0', '290.0', 'transistor', NULL, 'gen-viii', 'true', 'false', 'false', 'yellow', 'humanoid', 'no-eggs', NULL, 'slow', '3', '35', 'Electron PokÃ©mon', '472', 'This PokÃ©mon is a cluster of electrical energy. Itâ€™s said that removing the rings on Regielekiâ€™s body will unleash the PokÃ©monâ€™s latent power.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/894.png'),
