    ('896', 'Glastrier', 'Ice', NULL, '100', '145', '130', '65', '110', '30', '580', '2.2', '800.0', '290.0', 'chilling-neigh', NULL, 'gen-viii', 'true', 'false', 'false', 'white', 'quadruped', 'no-eggs', NULL, 'slow', '3', '35', 'Wild Horse PokÃ©mon', '474', 'Glastrier emits intense cold from its hooves. Itâ€™s also a belligerent PokÃ©monâ€”anything it wants, it takes by force.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/896.png'),
    ('897', 'Spectrier', 'Ghost', NULL, '100', '65', '60', '145', '80', '130', '580', '2.0', '44.5', '290.0', 'grim-neigh', NULL, 'gen-viii', 'true', 'false', 'false', 'black', 'quadruped', 'no-eggs', NULL, 'slow', '3', '35', 'Swift Horse PokÃ©mon', '475', 'It probes its surroundings with all its senses save oneâ€”it doesnâ€™t use its sense of sight. Spectrierâ€™s kicks are said to separate soul from body.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/897.png'),
    ('898', 'Calyrex', 'Psychic', 'Grass', '100', '80', '80', '80', '80', '80', '500', '1.1', '7.7', '250.0', 'unnerve', NULL, 'gen-viii', 'true', 'false', 'false', 'green', 'humanoid', 'no-eggs', NULL, 'slow', '3', '100', 'King PokÃ©mon', '476', 'Calyrex is a merciful PokÃ©mon, capable of providing healing and blessings. It reigned over the Galar region in times of yore.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/898.png'),
    ('899', 'Wyrdeer', 'Normal', 'Psychic', '103', '105', '72', '105', '75', '65', '525', '1.8', '95.1', '263.0', 'intimidate|frisk|sap-sipper', 'sap-sipper', 'gen-viii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'gray', 'quadruped', 'ground', NULL, 'slow', '135', '50', 'Big Horn PokÃ©mon', '120', 'The black orbs shine with an uncanny light when the PokÃ©mon is erecting invisible barriers. The fur shed from its beard retains heat well and is a highly useful material for winter clothing.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/899.png'),
    ('900', 'Kleavor', 'Bug', 'Rock', '70', '135', '95', '45', '70', '85', '500', '1.8', '89.0', '175.0', 'swarm|sheer-force|sharpness', 'sharpness', 'gen-viii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'brown', 'bug-wings', 'bug', NULL, 'medium', '115', '50', 'Axe PokÃ©mon', '58', 'A violent creature that fells towering trees with its crude axes and shields itself with hard stone. If one should chance upon this PokÃ©mon in the wilds, one''s only recourse is to flee.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/900.png'),
    ('901', 'Ursaluna', 'Ground', 'Normal', '130', '140', '105', '45', '80', '50', '550', '2.4', '290.0', '275.0', 'guts|bulletproof|unnerve', 'unnerve', 'gen-viii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'brown', 'quadruped', 'ground', NULL, 'medium', '75', '50', 'Peat PokÃ©mon', '110', 'I believe it was Hisui''s swampy terrain that gave Ursaluna its burly physique and newfound capacity to manipulate peat at will.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/901.png'),
    ('902', 'Basculegion-Male', 'Water', 'Ghost', '120', '112', '65', '80', '75', '78', '530', '3.0', '110.0', '265.0', 'swift-swim|adaptability|mold-breaker', 'mold-breaker', 'gen-viii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'green', 'fish', 'water2', NULL, 'medium', '135', '50', 'Big Fish PokÃ©mon', '280', 'Clads itself in the souls of comrades that perished before fulfilling their goals of journeying upstream. No other species throughout all Hisui''s rivers is Basculegion''s equal.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/902.png'),
    ('903', 'Sneasler', 'Fighting', 'Poison', '80', '130', '60', '40', '80', '120', '510', '1.3', '43.0', '102.0', 'pressure|unburden|poison-touch', 'poison-touch', 'gen-viii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'gray', 'upright', 'ground', NULL, 'medium-slow', '135', '50', 'Free Climb PokÃ©mon', '109', 'Because of Sneasler''s virulent poison and daunting physical prowess, no other species could hope to best it on the frozen highlands. Preferring solitude, this species does not form packs.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/903.png'),
    ('904', 'Overqwil', 'Dark', 'Poison', '85', '115', '95', '65', '65', '85', '510', '2.5', '60.5', '179.0', 'poison-point|swift-swim|intimidate', 'intimidate', 'gen-viii', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'black', 'fish', 'water2', NULL, 'medium', '135', '50', 'Pin Cluster PokÃ©mon', '106', 'Its lancelike spikes and savage temperament have earned it the nickname â€sea fiend.â€ It slurps up poison to nourish itself.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/904.png'),
    ('905', 'Enamorus-Incarnate', 'Fairy', 'Flying', '74', '115', '70', '135', '80', '106', '580', '1.6', '48.0', '116.0', 'cute-charm|contrary', 'contrary', 'gen-viii', 'true', 'false', 'false', 'pink', 'arms', 'no-eggs', NULL, 'slow', '3', '50', 'Love-Hate PokÃ©mon', '477', 'When it flies to this land from across the sea, the bitter winter comes to an end. According to legend, this PokÃ©mon''s love gives rise to the budding of fresh life across Hisui.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/905.png'),
