    ('918', 'Spidops', 'Bug', NULL, '60', '79', '92', '52', '86', '35', '404', '1.0', '16.5', '141.0', 'insomnia|stakeout', 'stakeout', 'gen-ix', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'green', 'armor', 'bug', NULL, 'slow-then-very-fast', '120', '50', 'Trap PokÃ©mon', '482', 'It clings to branches and ceilings using its threads and moves without a sound. It takes out its prey before the prey even notices it.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/918.png'),
    ('919', 'Nymble', 'Bug', NULL, '33', '46', '40', '21', '25', '45', '210', '0.2', '1.0', '42.0', 'swarm|tinted-lens', 'tinted-lens', 'gen-ix', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'gray', 'armor', 'bug', NULL, 'medium', '190', '20', 'Grasshopper PokÃ©mon', '483', 'It has its third set of legs folded up. When itâ€™s in a tough spot, this PokÃ©mon jumps over 30 feet using the strength of its legs.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/919.png'),
    ('920', 'Lokix', 'Bug', 'Dark', '71', '102', '78', '52', '55', '92', '450', '1.0', '17.5', '158.0', 'swarm|tinted-lens', 'tinted-lens', 'gen-ix', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'gray', 'humanoid', 'bug', NULL, 'medium', '30', '0', 'Grasshopper PokÃ©mon', '483', 'When it decides to fight all out, it stands on its previously folded legs to enter Showdown Mode. It neutralizes its enemies in short order.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/920.png'),
    ('921', 'Pawmi', 'Electric', NULL, '45', '50', '20', '40', '25', '60', '240', '0.3', '2.5', '48.0', 'static|natural-cure|iron-fist', 'iron-fist', 'gen-ix', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'yellow', 'quadruped', 'ground', NULL, 'medium', '190', '50', 'Mouse PokÃ©mon', '484', 'It has underdeveloped electric sacs on its cheeks. These sacs can produce electricity only if Pawmi rubs them furiously with the pads on its forepaws.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/921.png'),
    ('922', 'Pawmo', 'Electric', 'Fighting', '60', '75', '40', '50', '40', '85', '350', '0.4', '6.5', '123.0', 'volt-absorb|natural-cure|iron-fist', 'iron-fist', 'gen-ix', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'yellow', 'upright', 'ground', NULL, 'medium', '80', '50', 'Mouse PokÃ©mon', '484', 'When its group is attacked, Pawmo is the first to leap into battle, defeating enemies with a fighting technique that utilizes electric shocks.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/922.png'),
    ('923', 'Pawmot', 'Electric', 'Fighting', '70', '115', '70', '70', '60', '105', '490', '0.9', '41.0', '245.0', 'volt-absorb|natural-cure|iron-fist', 'iron-fist', 'gen-ix', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'yellow', 'upright', 'ground', NULL, 'medium', '45', '50', 'Hands-On PokÃ©mon', '484', 'This PokÃ©mon normally is slow to react, but once it enters battle, it will strike down its enemies with lightning-fast movements.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/923.png'),
    ('924', 'Tandemaus', 'Normal', NULL, '50', '50', '45', '40', '45', '75', '305', '0.3', '1.8', '61.0', 'run-away|pickup|own-tempo', 'own-tempo', 'gen-ix', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'white', 'heads', 'ground|fairy', NULL, 'fast', '150', '50', 'Couple PokÃ©mon', '485', 'Exhibiting great teamwork, they use their incisors to cut pieces out of any material that might be useful for a nest, then make off with them.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/924.png'),
