    ('926', 'Fidough', 'Fairy', NULL, '37', '55', '70', '30', '55', '65', '312', '0.3', '10.9', '62.0', 'own-tempo|klutz', 'klutz', 'gen-ix', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'yellow', 'quadruped', 'ground|mineral', NULL, 'medium-slow', '190', '50', 'Puppy PokÃ©mon', '486', 'This PokÃ©mon is smooth and moist to the touch. Yeast in Fidoughâ€™s breath induces fermentation in the PokÃ©monâ€™s vicinity.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/926.png'),
    ('927', 'Dachsbun', 'Fairy', NULL, '57', '80', '115', '50', '80', '95', '477', '0.5', '14.9', '167.0', 'well-baked-body|aroma-veil', 'aroma-veil', 'gen-ix', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'brown', 'quadruped', 'ground|mineral', NULL, 'medium-slow', '90', '50', 'Dog PokÃ©mon', '486', 'The pleasant aroma that emanates from this PokÃ©monâ€™s body helps wheat grow, so Dachsbun has been treasured by farming villages.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/927.png'),
    ('928', 'Smoliv', 'Grass', 'Normal', '41', '35', '45', '58', '51', '30', '260', '0.3', '6.5', '52.0', 'early-bird|harvest', 'harvest', 'gen-ix', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'green', 'legs', 'plant', NULL, 'medium-slow', '255', '50', 'Olive PokÃ©mon', '487', 'It protects itself from enemies by emitting oil from the fruit on its head. This oil is bitter and astringent enough to make someone flinch.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/928.png'),
