    ('938', 'Tadbulb', 'Electric', NULL, '61', '31', '41', '59', '35', '45', '272', '0.3', '0.4', '54.0', 'own-tempo|static|damp', 'damp', 'gen-ix', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'yellow', 'ball', 'water1', NULL, 'medium', '190', '50', 'EleTadpole PokÃ©mon', '491', 'Tadbulb shakes its tail to generate electricity. If it senses danger, it will make its head blink on and off to alert its allies.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/938.png'),
