    ('940', 'Wattrel', 'Electric', 'Flying', '40', '40', '35', '55', '40', '70', '280', '0.4', '3.6', '56.0', 'wind-power|volt-absorb|competitive', 'competitive', 'gen-ix', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'black', 'wings', 'water1|flying', NULL, 'medium-slow', '180', '50', 'Storm Petrel PokÃ©mon', '492', 'When its wings catch the wind, the bones within produce electricity. This PokÃ©mon dives into the ocean, catching prey by electrocuting them.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/940.png'),
    ('941', 'Kilowattrel', 'Electric', 'Flying', '70', '70', '60', '105', '60', '125', '490', '1.4', '38.6', '172.0', 'wind-power|volt-absorb|competitive', 'competitive', 'gen-ix', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'yellow', 'wings', 'water1|flying', NULL, 'medium-slow', '90', '50', 'Frigatebird PokÃ©mon', '492', 'Kilowattrel inflates its throat sac to amplify its electricity. By riding the wind, this PokÃ©mon can fly over 430 miles in a day.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/941.png'),
    ('942', 'Maschiff', 'Dark', NULL, '60', '78', '60', '40', '51', '51', '340', '0.5', '16.0', '68.0', 'intimidate|run-away|stakeout', 'stakeout', 'gen-ix', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'brown', 'quadruped', 'ground', NULL, 'medium-slow', '150', '50', 'Rascal PokÃ©mon', '493', 'It always scowls in an attempt to make opponents take it seriously, but even crying children will burst into laughter when they see Maschiffâ€™s face.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/942.png'),
