    ('944', 'Shroodle', 'Poison', 'Normal', '40', '65', '35', '40', '35', '75', '290', '0.2', '0.7', '58.0', 'unburden|pickpocket|prankster', 'prankster', 'gen-ix', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'gray', 'quadruped', 'ground', NULL, 'medium-slow', '190', '50', 'Toxic Mouse PokÃ©mon', '494', 'Though usually a mellow PokÃ©mon, it will sink its sharp, poison-soaked front teeth into any that anger it, causing paralysis in the object of its ire.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/944.png'),
    ('945', 'Grafaiai', 'Poison', 'Normal', '63', '95', '65', '80', '72', '110', '485', '0.7', '27.2', '170.0', 'unburden|poison-touch|prankster', 'prankster', 'gen-ix', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'gray', 'upright', 'ground', NULL, 'medium-slow', '90', '50', 'Toxic Monkey PokÃ©mon', '494', 'The color of the poisonous saliva depends on what the PokÃ©mon eats. Grafaiai covers its fingers in its saliva and draws patterns on trees in forests.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/945.png'),
    ('946', 'Bramblin', 'Grass', 'Ghost', '40', '65', '30', '45', '35', '60', '275', '0.6', '0.6', '55.0', 'wind-rider|infiltrator', 'infiltrator', 'gen-ix', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'brown', 'ball', 'plant', NULL, 'medium', '190', '50', 'Tumbleweed PokÃ©mon', '495', 'A soul unable to move on to the afterlife was blown around by the wind until it got tangled up with dried grass and became a PokÃ©mon.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/946.png'),
    ('947', 'Brambleghast', 'Grass', 'Ghost', '55', '115', '70', '80', '70', '90', '480', '1.2', '6.0', '168.0', 'wind-rider|infiltrator', 'infiltrator', 'gen-ix', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'brown', 'ball', 'plant', NULL, 'medium', '45', '50', 'Tumbleweed PokÃ©mon', '495', 'It will open the branches of its head to envelop its prey. Once it absorbs all the life energy it needs, it expels the prey and discards it.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/947.png'),
    ('948', 'Toedscool', 'Ground', 'Grass', '40', '40', '35', '50', '100', '70', '335', '0.9', '33.0', '67.0', 'mycelium-might', NULL, 'gen-ix', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'yellow', 'legs', 'plant', NULL, 'medium-slow', '190', '50', 'Woodear PokÃ©mon', '496', 'Toedscool lives in muggy forests. The flaps that fall from its body are chewy and very delicious.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/948.png'),
