    ('950', 'Klawf', 'Rock', NULL, '70', '100', '115', '35', '55', '75', '450', '1.3', '79.0', '158.0', 'anger-shell|shell-armor|regenerator', 'regenerator', 'gen-ix', 'false', 'false', 'false', 'red', 'armor', 'water3', NULL, 'medium', '120', '50', 'Ambush PokÃ©mon', '497', 'Klawf hangs upside-down from cliffs, waiting for prey. But Klawf canâ€™t remain in this position for long because its blood rushes to its head.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/950.png'),
